<style>
.container{
    min-height: 0 !important;
}
</style>
<div class="container mt-2">
    <h2 class="mb-3">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="accordion" id="faqAccordion">

        <!-- Question 1 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
                <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne">
                    How Do I Select a Product to Bid on or Purchase Directly?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Navigate to the Products Page
                            <ul><li>Browse through the available brands (e.g., Apple, Samsung, Xiaomi).</li></ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Choose a Brand
                            <ul><li>Click on the brand of your choice.</li></ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Select the Device Type
                            <ul><li>Based on the selected brand, choose the device category (e.g., iPad, iPhone for Apple).</li></ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Choose the Model
                            <ul><li>After selecting the device type, another menu will appear, allowing you to choose a specific model (e.g., iPhone 16 Pro Max).</li></ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>View Available Sellers
                            <ul>
                                <li>Country of Origin – The seller’s location.</li>
                                <li>SKU (Stock Keeping Unit) – A unique identifier for the product.</li>
                                <li>Seller Price – The listed price per unit.</li>
                                <li>Current Stock – The available quantity of the product.</li>
                                <li>Model Number – The official model identification.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 2 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo">
                    How Do I Purchase a Product Directly?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Select the Seller</li>
                        <li>Choose the Quantity
                            <ul>
                                <li>Click the plus (+) button to increase the quantity.</li>
                                <li>For bulk purchases, click on the displayed number in the quantity section and manually enter the desired amount.</li>
                                <li>The minimum order quantity starts at 1 unit and cannot exceed the seller's available stock.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Add the Product to Cart</li>
                        <li>Review Your Cart
                            <ul>
                                <li>The base price of the product.</li>
                                <li>The total cost, calculated based on the selected quantity.</li>
                                <li>A 15-minute timer, indicating the time limit to complete the checkout process.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Select a Forwarder</li>
                        <li>Proceed to Checkout</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 3 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree">
                    How Do I View My Order Status?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Go to the "My Orders" Page</li>
                        <li>Click on the Order Number</li>
                        <li>Check the Order Status
                            <ul>
                                <li>The order will initially be marked as Processing until the seller ships the product.</li>
                                <li>Once the item is shipped, the status will change to Completed.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Download the Order Details</li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 4 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour">
                    How Do I Consolidate My Orders?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Go to the "My Orders" Page</li>
                        <li>Select the Checkboxes</li>
                        <li>Conditions for Order Consolidation:
                            <ul>
                                <li>Same Seller – Orders must be from the same seller to be eligible for consolidation.</li>
                                <li>Same Forwarder – The selected orders must be shipped using the same forwarder.</li>
                                <li>Same Purchase Date – Orders must have been placed on the same day to qualify for consolidation.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Question 5 -->
        <div class="accordion-item">
            <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFive">
                <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFive" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFive">
                    How Do I Place a Bid on a Product?
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="collapseFive" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFive" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                <div class="accordion-body">
                    <ol>
                        <li>Follow the Product Selection Steps</li>
                        <li>Set the Quantity</li>
                        <li>Submit Your Bid</li>
                        <li>Select a Forwarder</li>
                        <li>Bid Restrictions
                            <ul>
                                <li>Your bid price cannot be lower than 5% of the seller's listed price.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                        <li>Track Your Bids</li>
                        <li>Bid Responses
                            <ul>
                                <li>Accepted – The seller has approved your bid, and you can proceed with the purchase.</li>
                                <li>Rejected – The seller has declined your bid.</li>
                                <li>Countered – The seller has submitted a counteroffer, which you can review and respond to.</li>
                            </ul>
                        </li>
                    </ol>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>